{"tid":2391765,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"500萬訂閱美保守派主持人克勞德(Steven Crowder)宣布起訴Facebook！！！！！","createTime":"2021-02-02T11:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T18:07:13.000Z","uid":88743,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"374436ef0b6afd54184d8aec85f038f85b56db70","tid":2391765,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T11:42:34.000Z","msg":"Steven Crowder Channel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/StevenCrowder\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FStevenCrowder&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BCNNnhsiPIcvur842Fp1uB0%3D&h=1a32b5fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/StevenCrowder</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bitchute.com/channel/stevencrowder/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bitchute.com%2Fchannel%2Fstevencrowder%2F&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BCNNnhsiPIcvur842Fp1uB0%3D&h=5f93029c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bitchute.com/channel/stevencrowder/</a><br />\n<br />\nSteven Crowder To Sue Facebook For &lsquo;Unfair&rsquo; Treatment Of Conservatives <br />\n<a href=\"https://dailycaller.com/2021/02/01/steven-crowder-sue-facebook-unfair-treatment-conservatives/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdailycaller.com%2F2021%2F02%2F01%2Fsteven-crowder-sue-facebook-unfair-treatment-conservatives%2F&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BCNNnhsiPIcvur842Fp1uB0%3D&h=5cb3ecc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://dailycaller.com/2021/02/01/steven-crowder-sue-facebook-unfair-treatment-conservatives/</a><br />\n<br />\n美保守派主持人克勞德宣布起訴臉書<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/2/2/n12727046.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F21%2F2%2F2%2Fn12727046.htm&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BCNNnhsiPIcvur842Fp1uB0%3D&h=db35a42d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/2/2/n12727046.htm</a><br />\n   \t \t \t \t  <br />\n 【大紀元2021年02月02日訊】（英文大紀元記者費翰報導／高杉編譯）美國保守派主持人史蒂文&middot;克勞德（Steven Crowder）週一透露，他已經起訴臉書（Facebook），指控其<strong><span class=\"red\">「不正當競爭、欺詐、虛假廣告和反壟斷。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n 克勞德的律師比爾&middot;里奇蒙德（Bill Richmond）在克勞德的YouTube頻道上表示，該訴訟<strong><span class=\"red\">「已經被提起」</span></strong>，指控這家科技巨頭公司「虛假廣告、違反反壟斷法、不正當競爭和欺詐」。<br />\n<br />\n 克勞德在其網頁上表示：「關鍵的糾正措施是禁令救濟（停止不公平／欺騙行為）。我們還要求賠償七位數的金錢損失，這樣做的目的是迫使其政策的實施和執行能夠保持誠實性和清晰度。」「我們的觀點是，我們支持企業，但反對欺詐。臉書承諾在執行其政策時不涉及政治、種族或宗教偏見，以此引誘消費者和創作者花錢、提供數據和觀點，但他們卻明裡暗裡都這麼做了，因此我們提起了這場訴訟。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"> 在YouTube視頻中，克勞德說他於去年11月3日的選舉直播在報導過程中被突然切斷了。克勞德說，他從未被告知為什麼這個直播會被封殺。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n 他說：<span class=\"red\"><strong>「他們毫無理由地從有史以來最大的平台上，刪除了有史以來最大的流量。」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n 《大紀元時報》已經聯繫Facebook請其就此置評。<br />\n<br />\n 克勞德的網站還指責說，臉書故意減少了對某些頁面的訪問量，並偏袒某些新聞媒體。<br />\n 1月6日國會大廈發生騷亂後，包括時任總統唐納德&middot;川普（特朗普）在內的一些保守派人士被臉書和其它社交媒體平台封殺。多年來，保守派一直抱怨大型科技公司審查或扼殺右翼新聞網站和頁面，促使川普和其他人考慮廢除《通信規範法案》中的第230條款。該條款是社交媒體網站和其它網站的內容免責保護傘。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"> 克勞德的網站稱：「我們已經準備好將這起訴訟提交到任何需要的地方，包括美國最高法院。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n 克勞德週日（1月31日）下午在推特上提到了這起訴訟：「我不知道2月2日會發生什麼。但是明天，我們將不會再自我審查，我們不會再被欺負，被壓制或者被恐嚇。我們不會向任何人下跪。」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"> <strong>2020年11月，保守派評論員坎迪斯&middot;歐文斯（Candace Owens）宣布起訴臉書公司的「事實核查員」，其中包括《今日美國》（USA Today）和《頭條新聞》（Lead stories）&mdash;&mdash;<span class=\"xx-large\">部分資金來自與中國共產黨有聯繫的「字節跳動」（ByteDance）公司。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n 歐文斯當時表示：「現在是事實核實這些事實核查員的時候了。」「我要讓這些傢伙也經歷事實核查，弄清楚他們與臉書之間的關係。」<br />\n<br />\n 克勞德的訴訟案將提交加利福尼亞州北部地區的美國地方法院。<br />\n<br />\n 責任編輯：葉紫微#"},{"pid":"7c04d02b01652233c49350d0557f6280e01664fd","tid":2391765,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721ab6c7b8c5ad7f235e6caaf48e265280e15270","tid":2391765,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"終於出返嚟 佢好似身體有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349b9c2ace8d2b7a38f80336632eea57ee1423c3","tid":2391765,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4335ad79f5bc1d33cadf357e7e8ebc6bd9493d8","tid":2391765,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"721ab6c7b8c5ad7f235e6caaf48e265280e15270","tid":2391765,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"終於出返嚟 佢好似身體有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T18:07:13.000Z","msg":"好似話老婆流產同佢個心有事"}]}